PrecisAppointment of Mervyn C. Russell, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as chairman of the board of directors of the Halifax Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and approval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Mervyn C. Russell, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as a part-time director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Donald Parker, whose term has expired.
